title: Bryant doesn't go with Cowboys to NY, less likely to play (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,486 Bryant doesn't go with Cowboys to NY, less likely to play (Yahoo Sports) IRVING, Texas (AP) -- Dez Bryant didn't travel with the Cowboys to New York, making it less likely the All-Pro receiver will return from a broken right foot against the Giants.
